THE ART OF WAR · node WAR · WAR · THE ART OF WAR · polemos · strategy through the ages · UD0 / polemos

universe of origin : a sphere of the field of conflict
seal               : War is older than writing, and so is the attempt to think it through. From Sun Tzu's deceptions to Clausewitz's friction to the cold calculus of the nuclear age, strategy is the art of bending force to a purpose — winning, ideally, without fighting; and when fighting, of seeing the whole board while the enemy sees only their own piece.
